---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ShapeFooter from "../../components/ShapeFooter.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Chuong trinh doi tac NocoBase - Phat trien kinh doanh cung NocoBase"
  description="Tham gia chuong trinh doi tac NocoBase. Tao doanh thu tu kenh ban hang va giu tron doanh thu dich vu. Hai mo hinh linh hoat danh cho tich hop he thong, tu van va don vi cung cap dich vu."
  keywords="NocoBase partner, chuong trinh doi tac, doi tac kenh, doi tac dich vu, reseller, tich hop he thong"
>
  <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 text-center"><div class="title-heading"><span class="badge bg-soft-primary mb-3">Chuong trinh doi tac</span><h1 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">Phat trien kinh doanh<br/>cung NocoBase</h1><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted">Hai mo hinh hop tac linh hoat cho phan phoi, trien khai hoac ket hop ca hai. Cung nhau phat trien.</p><div class="mt-4 pt-2"><a href="mailto:partner@nocobase.com" class="btn btn-primary me-3"><i class="uil uil-envelope me-1"></i>Lien he</a><a href="#partnership-models" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="uil uil-arrow-down me-1"></i>Xem them</a></div></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="partnership-models">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12"><div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2"><h4 class="title mb-4">Hai mo hinh hop tac linh hoat</h4><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Chon mot mo hinh hoac ket hop ca hai de mo rong doanh thu</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded h-100 p-4"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"><div class="icons text-start me-3"><i class="uil uil-store rounded h3 mb-0 text-primary"></i></div><h5 class="mb-0">Phan phoi kenh</h5></div><p class="text-muted">Quang ba va ban san pham NocoBase de tao doanh thu tu kenh ban hang.</p><ul class="list-unstyled"><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Co che hoa hong linh hoat</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Tich luy lau dai theo ket qua kinh doanh</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Ho tro va tai lieu ban hang day du</span></li></ul></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded h-100 p-4"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"><div class="icons text-start me-3"><i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0 text-primary"></i></div><h5 class="mb-0">Dich vu trien khai</h5></div><p class="text-muted">Cung cap trien khai, tuy chinh, tich hop va dao tao de tao doanh thu theo du an.</p><ul class="list-unstyled"><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Ban giu tron doanh thu dich vu</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Chu dong xay dung mo hinh dich vu rieng</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Co hoi uu tien o cap doi tac cao hon</span></li></ul></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12"><div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2"><h4 class="title mb-4">Cach chung toi ho tro ban</h4><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Nguon luc va ho tro de doi tac tang truong cung NocoBase</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-file-alt h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Ho tro kinh doanh</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Tai lieu ban hang, noi dung va case study</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-headphones h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Ho tro ky thuat</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Kenh ho tro danh rieng cho doi tac</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-users-alt h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Co hoi gioi thieu</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Co hoi khach hang duoc chuyen tu NocoBase</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-award h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Su dung thuong hieu</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Xac nhan chinh thuc va co hoi dong marketing</p></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12 text-center"><h4 class="title mb-4">San sang tro thanh doi tac?</h4><p class="text-muted para-desc mx-auto mb-4">Tham gia he sinh thai doi tac cong nghe dang mo rong cung NocoBase.</p></div></div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded overflow-hidden"><iframe src="https://service-en.nocobase.com/public-forms/rl8c0cnkyzx" style="width: 100%; min-height: 700px; border: none;" loading="lazy"></iframe></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ShapeFooter />
</Layout>
